name: doorbellsound
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: doorbell sound
des:
Ding dong! There's nothing like the sweet sound of company arriving at your doorstep!

 From old-fashioned doorbells to modern rings and buzzers, this skill has them all! These sounds may conjure up nostalgia of guests arriving for a holiday meal, or the excitement of a surprise visit!

Play the doorbell sound and watch as they answer the door to find no one there. Repeat various times for optimal humor!
Ring the bell and open the door to life with fun doorbell sounds today!

Have Alexa ring the doorbell for you.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
